If you have the Spellcasting or Pact Magic class feature, the spells on the Mark of Passage Spells table are added to that feature's spell list.
Mark of Passage Spells:
1 | {@spell Expeditious Retreat|XPHB}, {@spell Jump|XPHB}
2 | {@spell Find Steed|XPHB}, {@spell Pass without Trace|XPHB}
3 | {@spell Blink|XPHB}, {@spell Phantom Steed|XPHB}
4 | {@spell Dimension Door|XPHB}, {@spell Freedom of Movement|XPHB}
5 | {@spell Teleportation Circle|XPHB}

You gain the following benefits.
